<LegalShell
  title="Privacy Policy — Enjoy 24h"
  description="How Enjoy 24h handles personal information."
>
  <div class="legal-page__eyebrow">Legal</div>
  <h1>Privacy <span class="accent">Policy.</span></h1>
  <div class="legal-page__updated">Last updated · 1 May 2026</div>

  <p>
    Enjoy 24h (&quot;we&quot;, &quot;us&quot;, &quot;our&quot;) respects your privacy. This page explains what information we collect when you visit our website or shop, why we collect it, and what we do with it.
  </p>

  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <p>Our website does not require you to create an account, sign in, or submit personal information to browse. We collect minimal data:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Basic analytics</strong> — anonymized data about pages visited, referring sources, and rough geographic region (city/country level), used only to understand how the site is used.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Age verification</strong> — we store a flag in your browser confirming you've passed our age check. This stays on your device only and is never sent to us.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Communication you initiate</strong> — if you call or message us directly, we keep what you send us only as long as needed to respond.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What we don't collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>We don't sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties for marketing.</li>
    <li>We don't track you across other websites.</li>
    <li>We don't profile you or build advertising audiences from your visits.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>In-store privacy</h2>
  <p>
    When you visit our shop in person, we may keep records of cannabis purchases as required by Thai law, including age verification documentation. These records are kept secure and are only shared with authorities when legally required.
  </p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    We use minimal browser storage — only what's needed to remember your age verification choice during a session and to make the site function. We do not use advertising cookies or third-party trackers.
  </p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>
    You may ask us what information we hold about you, request that it be corrected, or ask us to delete it. To do so, contact us at the phone number below.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>
    If we change this policy, we'll update the date at the top. Material changes will be highlighted on the site for a reasonable period.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about this policy or your data?<br />
    <strong>Phone:</strong>
    <a href="https://wa.me/66993594534" class="legal-page__inline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">099 359 4534</a><br />
    <strong>Address:</strong> Q8R9+H3V, Rawai, Mueang Phuket District, Phuket 83100, Thailand
  </p>
</LegalShell>
